---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import siteConfig from '@/site-config'
import '@/styles/typing.css'
---

<BaseLayout description={siteConfig.description}>
  <article class="prose lg:prose-xl">
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      Greetings! My name is
      <b class="text-white-600">Hidayat Taufiqur</b>
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-md typing-animation">
      ðŸš€ Junior D365FO Developer | Software Engineer
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
      I'm a Software Engineer who recently graduated from Telkom University with
      a Computer Science degree. I'm currently working as a Junior Developer
      specializing in Dynamics 365 Finance and Operations (D365FO), but my true
      passion lies in backend engineering and system architecture.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
      My interests span across various domains within Software Engineering, a
      particular focus on <b
        >Backend Development, System Engineering, DevOps, and Distributed
        Systems</b
      >. I'm constantly exploring new technologies and methodologies to expand
      my skillset in these areas.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
      Throughout my academic and professional journey, I have gained hands-on
      experience with a variety of technologies such as
      <span class="font-semibold">
        <b
          >Linux, C, C++, SQL, Java, Python, Flask, MongoDB, PostgreSQL, Redis,
          NodeJS, Golang, Laravel, GCP, Nix, Notion, Nginx, X++, D365 Finance
          and Operations, and n8n</b
        >
      </span>.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
      Beyond my technical pursuits, I enjoy <b>
        watching movies, jamming to music, playing guitar, playing games (mostly
        Valorant, FIFA, or Mobile Legends), and tinkering around with my
        day-to-day work environment</b
      >. Feel free to explore around to learn more about my work, projects, and
      interests.
    </p>

    <p class="text-lg mt-8">
      Interested in learning more about my professional background? Please check
      my <b>
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XiM2WTfmVllMGRBhwis-Bgl9DPlVrKcC/view?usp=sharing"
          target="_blank"
          aria-label="View my CV/resume">CV/resume!</a
        >
      </b>
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 p-3 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-sm">
        ðŸ’¼ While I'm currently focused on ERP development, I'm actively seeking
        opportunities in backend engineering and system architecture roles.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <p class="text-lg">Let's connect:</p>
      <div class="flex gap-x-4 gap-y-2 flex-wrap mt-4">
        {
          siteConfig.socialLinks.map((link) => (
            <a
              aria-label={link.text}
              href={link.href}
              target="_blank"
              class="prose-link text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center p-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700"
            >
              <i class:list={[link.icon]} class="text-xl mr-2" />
              {link.text}
            </a>
          ))
        }
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg">
        Or email me at
        <a
          class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200"
          aria-label={siteConfig.email}
          href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}
        >
          {siteConfig.email}
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
